Convention country or Bunkers Convention country resulting 
from the discharge or escape;

(a)  a Liability Convention country to enforce a claim in respect 
of  a  liability  incurred  under  any  provision  corresponding  to 
section 3;

(c)  to provide for the cancellation and delivery up of a certificate 
issued  in  such  circumstances  as  may  be  prescribed  by  the 
regulations;

(e)  to  provide  for  the  conversion  of  the  special  drawing  rights 
referred to in this Act into the amount of money expressed in 
Ringgit Malaysia;

